    "body": "# EVM Modification Strategy\r\n\r\nThe geth EVM support configuration via the [go-ethereum/core/vm.Config](https://godoc.org/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/vm#Config) type and more specifically the JumpTable.\r\n\r\nSince I haven't seen any thorough discussion on how/when includes them I propose for now to use a specific EVM configuration for the sharding client that would includes the new opcodes (more information in ethereum/vyper#632).",
